{
  "texts": [
    "Note that all results for this subsection are from FT-Seq (BERT) with DELD.The low values of the Forgetting (Fgt) metric across different datasets demonstrate the effectiveness of our method in mitigating catastrophic forgetting.",
    "Note that a negative forgetting value indicates a performance improvement after final training.",
    "We speculate this is because the model successfully transfers knowledge from other datasets.",
    "By sequentially concatenating the learned soft prompts, DELD retains knowledge from previous datasets while adapting to new ones.",
    "These findings reinforce the practical viability of DELD for detecting evolving LLM-generated disinformation that requires continual adaptation without sacrificing previously acquired knowledge."
  ]
}